The paper discusses machine learning algorithms and their implementation on mobile phones, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and distributed computing (cs.Distributed). The paper also mentions image processing and optimization, which could fall under the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and data compression (cs.DC).
